Regulations Amending the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS (POWER-ASSISTED
BICYCLES) which introduce and define the term "power-assisted bicycle" and
exempt them from compliance with the standards for the limited-speed
motorcycle sub-class.
